    <date year="2001" month="February" day="5"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>The DIAMETER base protocol is intended to provide a AAA framework for Mobile-IP, NASREQ and ROAMOPS. This draft specifies the message format, transport, error reporting and security services to be used by all DIAMETER extensions and MUST be supported by all DIAMETER implementations.</t>
    </abstract>
